&lt;p&gt;We are seeking to recruit Band 6 Nurse Practitioner to join our team of highly skilled Specialist Nurses within Eden Court Enhanced Care Facility. The team works in partnership with Akari Care providing multidisciplinary assessments of older frailer people who require rehabilitation programme in order to facilitate discharge back home.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Patients step down from hospital or step up from community as hospital admission avoidance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We provide reciprocal support to Connie Lewcock Resource Centre.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The service is provided over 7 days&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please refer to the Job Description and Person Specification for all essential and desirable criteria required for the role. A current driving licence is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Part Time 16 Hours/Week&lt;/p&gt;
